headline: Eaton Announces the Planned Transition of Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Olivier Leonetti, Effective April 1, 2026
summary: DUBLIN, November 20, 2025--Intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) today announced that Olivier Leonetti, executive vice president and chief financial officer, will be leaving Eaton on April 1, 2026, as part of a planned transition.
